snippet.title: Home Runtaro (iOS) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
This turned out to be a longplay of Home Runtaro, from the makers of the semi-famous "Hidden My Game By Mom" game of similar sight gags. 

In Home Runtaro, you're tasked with slapping dingers off of various kooky characters across fifty different levels.
